                h4 Technologies:
                p Harmonic Analysis.
              li
                h4 Description:
                p
                  | In Harmonic Analysis and other fields we are interested in breaking a signal into pieces.
                  | To generalize the Fourier decomposition, and measure physical quantities other than the frequency content of a signal, we may decompose a signal into the spectrum of a general self adjoint operator.
                  | It is interesting to study the relationship between the spread in energy in the original domain and the new domain defined by the operator. This paper explores a generalization of the celebrated Heisenberg Uncertainty Principle from Quantum Mechanics.
